{"word":"πέραν","slug":"πέραν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πέραν</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>περάω</el> ‘go directly through’] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b>on the other side<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as noun <el>τὸ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πέραν\">πέραν</a></el> the shore/land on the other side <b><a href='B:470 8:18'>Mt 8:18</a>, <a href='B:470 8:28'>28</a>; <a href='B:470 14:22'>14:22</a>; <a href='B:470 16:5'>16:5</a>; <a href='B:480 4:35'>Mk 4:35</a>; <a href='B:480 6:45'>6:45</a>; <a href='B:480 8:13'>8:13</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prep.\">prep.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><a href='B:500 1:28'>J 1:28</a>; <a href='B:500 3:26'>3:26</a>; <a href='B:500 10:40'>10:40</a>.</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πέραν\">πέραν</a> τοῦ Ἰορδάνου</el> on the other side (= east) of the Jordan <b><a href='B:470 4:15'>Mt 4:15</a>, <a href='B:470 4:25'>25</a>; <a href='B:470 19:1'>19:1</a>; <a href='B:480 3:8'>Mk 3:8</a>; <a href='B:480 10:1'>10:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:περαιτέρω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πέρας\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}